Achievements.Name: Back to business
Achievements.Description: You support the local weapon trade. That's... well, nice of you.

Achievements.Name: King of the arena
Achievements.Description: You fought like a lion and ended up victorious in the Row.

Achievements.Name: Nobody's perfect
Achievements.Description: The Imperial officer in the Monastery seemed to be of good faith. Just to be safe, you offed him.

Achievements.Name: Warrior
Achievements.Description: You have valiantly dealt with all the trials in Of Orcs and Men

Achievements.Name: I'm a killer
Achievements.Description: You slit 47 throats and they never saw it coming. So you dig?

Achievements.Name: You crack me up
Achievements.Description: You have a delicate tendency to break the bones of people who get in your way, so congratulations.

Achievements.Name: Big chest lover
Achievements.Description: So you went digging around in every corner to find at least twenty chests to empty, huh?

Achievements.Name: Jack of all blades
Achievements.Description: You hit eight enemies with a single blow. Huh, not bad.

Achievements.Name: Guidance counselor
Achievements.Description: You were able to find the best people for your squad for the assault on the Pillar.

Achievements.Name: Smart and smarter
Achievements.Description: You chose to improve one of your Skills before you learned another one. Kudos for that.

Achievements.Name: Poisoner
Achievements.Description: You don't like wasting perfectly good poison, so you cleaned your blade off on 3 different enemies.

Achievements.Name: Go bling-bling
Achievements.Description: You only wear upgraded equipment. It's a matter of reputation.

Achievements.Name: I know a shortcut
Achievements.Description: The good thing with shortcuts is that they are faster. It would seem you got that right.

Achievements.Name: Deratizator
Achievements.Description: You cut short the Goblin invasion in the shantytown. Pretty violently.

Achievements.Name: A hair too late
Achievements.Description: You pulled your girlfriend Brune out of trouble. She owes you a massage for that.

Achievements.Name: Well trained
Achievements.Description: You got even with the Trainer. And he got dead.

Achievements.Name: One less nutcase
Achievements.Description: You avenged your friend and killed the mad Shaman. He'll guide the dead himself.

Achievements.Name: Hand shake
Achievements.Description: You showed those Black Hands who's the boss.

Achievements.Name: Off the Wall
Achievements.Description: You finally got past that damn Wall ! Well done !

Achievements.Name: Class struggle
Achievements.Description: You avoided a miners' revolt. Thanks to you, they will be able to die for a nobler cause.

Achievements.Name: Throat-slitter
Achievements.Description: You sent Styx to introduce his daggers to the sentinels of the Mire. He thanks you.

Achievements.Name: I don't like chit-chat
Achievements.Description: You didn't feel like letting Gorkash bore you with his bull, so you cut him off.

Achievements.Name: No quarter
Achievements.Description: You have imposed your authority by taking out all opposing Orcs. An age-old method that still works.

Achievements.Name: Samaritan
Achievements.Description: In a spirit of forgiveness as heroic as it was delusional, you decided to spare Dakath the traitor.

Achievements.Name: All this for that
Achievements.Description: You had to put up with a pile of enraged Goblins, but you got your flask of water!

Achievements.Name: The beast and the beast
Achievements.Description: Garok is now your friend for life. Now that's a sign of upcoming great conversations!

Achievements.Name: You mythed!
Achievements.Description: You showed that big-mouth Braggart that when he blows his own horn he's talking to the wrong guy!

Achievements.Name: Team spirit
Achievements.Description: You made sure to put together a special team to assault the Pillar from the Mire.

Achievements.Name: In open air
Achievements.Description: You managed to escape the Mire. With the chick, too.

Achievements.Name: Slicer-Dicer
Achievements.Description: You decided to forget your past to devote yourself to a career as an Assassin. Enjoy.

Achievements.Name: Into the shadow
Achievements.Description: You decided that black magic isn't so bad, especially when you're the only one who knows it.

Achievements.Name: Inner rage
Achievements.Description: You turned Arkail into a berserk monster. More than before, that is. And it went well. For some.

Achievements.Name: Anger management
Achievements.Description: You helped Arkail control his rage. Those of his friends and family who are still alive thank you.

Achievements.Name: I've got my friends in my head
Achievements.Description: You've gone through nightmares, but now you're finally setting off for the Island of Laments.

Achievements.Name: Regicide the first
Achievements.Description: Youâ€™ve killed Emperor Damocles. Which is nice to hear, â€˜cause that was the idea in the first place.

Achievements.Name: Your sister too
Achievements.Description: You have taken on the most formidable warriors in the Empire. Apart from you, of course.

Achievements.Name: Repeat offender
Achievements.Description: You killed the Emperor again, and set fire to the Tower. Maybe you should stop now.

Achievements.Name: Rakash
Achievements.Description: You have smoothly dealt with all the trials in Of Orcs and Men

Achievements.Name: Mercenary
Achievements.Description: You have bravely dealt with all the trials in Of Orcs and Men

Achievements.Name: Bloodjaw
Achievements.Description: You dealt with all the trials in Of Orcs and Men like a berserker.

Achievements.Name: The hard way
Achievements.Description: You handled your first quarrel like... an Orc. Well, you sure got into your character!

Achievements.Name: Talk it out
Achievements.Description: You allowed Styx to calm things down before Arkail went berserk. Literally.

Achievements.Name: Manual worker
Achievements.Description: Nice move, you sliced up a boss without a single auto attack!

Achievements.Name: To each his branch
Achievements.Description: As a good specialist, you've decided to learn every skill in a single tree.

Achievements.Name: My house!
Achievements.Description: As a good master, you've decided to learn and perfect each Skill in a single tree.
